text: Gulod railway station is a proposed new railway station on the South Main Line (Southrail) of the Philippine National Railways. This PNR station is proposed by the JICA for both the current Metro Commuter and the South Line of the North-South Commuter Rail Project. The station will be located in between the existing Cabuyao station and Mamatid station at Gulod, Cabuyao City, Laguna. ==References== Category:Philippine National Railways stations Category:Railway stations in Laguna (province) Category:Buildings and structures in Cabuyao
title: Gulod railway station
